================================================================================
                           LICENSING INFORMATION
================================================================================

This entire project is licensed under MIT License.

The MIT License was chosen to maximize compatibility and allow free commercial
and non-commercial use. All core dependencies use permissive licenses 
(MIT, Apache-2.0, BSD) that are compatible with MIT.

Key Computer Vision Dependencies:
  - YOLOX (Apache-2.0) - Object detection (vehicle, pedestrian)
  - DETR (Apache-2.0) - Accident detection via HuggingFace Transformers
  - PyTorch (BSD-style) - Deep learning framework

================================================================================
                        THIRD-PARTY LICENSES
