This project uses the following third-party libraries:

YOLOX by Megvii
  License: Apache-2.0
  Website: https://github.com/Megvii-BaseDetection/YOLOX
  Note: Used for vehicle and pedestrian detection

DETR Traffic Accident Detection
  License: Apache-2.0
  Model: hilmantm/detr-traffic-accident-detection
  Website: https://huggingface.co/hilmantm/detr-traffic-accident-detection
  Note: Used for accident detection

HuggingFace Transformers
  License: Apache-2.0
  Website: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers
  Note: Used to load and run DETR model

